          "reviewBody": "This is probably the one and only school Kolkata thats believes and takes up the responsibility of the overall  development and welfare of the students.\nWe have been associated with them since 2015 for the annual dental awareness program. Dentists Day at the school is very executed, very meticulously year after year.\n\nKudos  the BGES team and authorities,\nDr P.S Sethi\nDontia Dental Care\nElgin Road",
