          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It is the best school that I ever have known. The best school in Bhawanipore. Has the best teachers and principal. Teachers are both strict and nice. Best thing about this school is that it's classes,  staff rooms are all air-conditioned. They teach you reply nicely. Teachers are like our bff.\nLove the school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "THE BGES SCHOOL - Sreepally,Bhowanipore"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Gautam Hazra"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-09-12",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It was established by a trust of commercial Gujarati men in 1928. J. J. Ajmera donated a lump sum money for construction of school buildings. Earlier it was known as J. J. Ajmera High school. It's a co-educational, private and  English medium school. The Higher Secondary was founded in 1960. It's affiliated by ICSE Board. It has a computer training centre. Infrastructure and faculty are good. It's standard and performance are satisfied. Ex-students are Dilip Doshi, famous spin bowler, Dilip Sanghvi, founder Sun Pharma etc etc.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "THE BGES SCHOOL - Sreepally,Bhowanipore"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Renu Shah"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-08-08",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have studied in this school for about 12 years. I feel that teachers are best at their respective subjects. My childhood which i lived in this school are the most memorable days of my life i wish that i could live that kind of life again....\nWhen it comes to discipline and administration i think they are the best..\nHeadmaster sir is very strict.The only thing that should had been better was sports facilities.. A school must have a big ground to play all kinds of sport and also dedicated and professional sports teachers....\nI LOVED THE JOURNEY OF 12 YEARS ❤❤❤❤",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
