            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I study in this school,nice not that many facilities, they can check Ur bag whenever they want and can give any punishment like sitting on a small tool for a week and stuff like that. Some teachers are offcourse strict but some very good. A little bias but that is the case with every school . Overall a nice school with a good headmaster but strict headmistress , most of the teachers are the best u can find , some very fun but some strict .",
